      "span_text": "The method is understood as an important 'key starting point' in CA/MCA research, as it is 'sufficient to attract attention and analytic interest because the instance is an event whose features and structures can be examined to discover how it is organised' (Psathas, 1995, p. 50) and 'orderly for its participants' [CITATION_1] ."
